# Workflow

Never start implementing immediately.

Follow this order:

1. Understand the feature.
2. Read the Flight Manual.
3. Inspect existing implementation.
4. Search for similar code.
5. Reuse existing architecture.
6. Implement.
7. Run tests.
8. Run build.
9. Summarize changes.

Never rewrite large portions of the application unless explicitly requested.

Prefer incremental improvements.
